		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Staff, Very Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p>This staff can be wielded as a magic Quarterstaff that grants a +3 bonus to attack rolls and damage rolls made with it.</p><p><strong>Activation</strong> - 10 Charges (Regains [[/r 1d6+4]] Charges at Dawn)</p><ul><li><p>While holding the staff, you can expend 1 or more charges to activate one of the following magical effects using your spell save DC:</p><ul><li><p>No Action (1 - 3 Charges) - When you hit with a melee attack using it, you can expend up to 3 charges. For each charge you expend, the target takes an extra [[/damage 1d6 Force]] damage.</p></li></ul></li><li><p>If you expend the last charge, roll [[/r 1d20]]. On a 1, the staff becomes a nonmagical @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.qpOD3sz47K9lnNgt]{Quarterstaff}.</p></li></ul>",
